ref=\"#cb4-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">1</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb4-3\"><a href=\"#cb4-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">0</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb4-4\"><a href=\"#cb4-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">1</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb4-5\"><a href=\"#cb4-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">========</span> EXPECT</span>\n<span id=\"cb4-6\"><a href=\"#cb4-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>you need to login first</span>\n<span id=\"cb4-7\"><a href=\"#cb4-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;</span> FINISH</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb5\"><pre class=\"sourceCode py\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb5-1\"><a href=\"#cb5-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> INSERT</span>\n<span id=\"cb5-2\"><a href=\"#cb5-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">1</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb5-3\"><a href=\"#cb5-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">0</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb5-4\"><a href=\"#cb5-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">0</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb5-5\"><a href=\"#cb5-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">========</span> EXPECT</span>\n<span id=\"cb5-6\"><a href=\"#cb5-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>you need to login first</span>\n<span id=\"cb5-7\"><a href=\"#cb5-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;</span> FINISH</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb6\"><pre class=\"sourceCode py\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb6-1\"><a href=\"#cb6-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> INSERT</span>\n<span id=\"cb6-2\"><a href=\"#cb6-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">1</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb6-3\"><a href=\"#cb6-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">1</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb6-4\"><a href=\"#cb6-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">0</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb6-5\"><a href=\"#cb6-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">========</span> EXPECT</span>\n<span id=\"cb6-6\"><a href=\"#cb6-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>you must to login <span class=\"im\">as</span> admin</span>\n<span id=\"cb6-7\"><a href=\"#cb6-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;</span> FINISH</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb7\"><pre class=\"sourceCode py\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb7-1\"><a href=\"#cb7-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> INSERT</span>\n<span id=\"cb7-2\"><a href=\"#cb7-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">1</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb7-3\"><a href=\"#cb7-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">1</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb7-4\"><a href=\"#cb7-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dv\">1</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb7-5\"><a href=\"#cb7-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">========</span> EXPECT</span>\n<span id=\"cb7-6\"><a href=\"#cb7-6\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>done</span>\n<span id=\"cb7-7\"><a href=\"#cb7-7\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;</span> FINISH</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"dicas\">Dicas</h2>\n<h3 id=\"programando-em-c\">Programando em: C</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\u00c9 poss\u00edvel utilizar verifica\u00e7\u00f5es simples para verificar cada\ncondi\u00e7\u00e3o individualmente. Em valores booleanos, 0 \u00e9 considerado falso\n(<code>false</code>) e qualquer valor diferente de 0 \u00e9 verdadeiro\n(<code>true</code>). O s\u00edmbolo <code>!</code> indica a nega\u00e7\u00e3o de uma\ncondi\u00e7\u00e3o, ou seja, espera-se que a condi\u00e7\u00e3o seja falsa:</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb8\"><pre class=\"sourceCode c\"><code class=\"sourceCode c\"><span id=\"cb8-1\"><a href=\"#cb8-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"dt\">int</span> main<span class=\"op\">()</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb8-2\"><a href=\"#cb8-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"op\">(!</span>wifi<span class=\"op\">)</span> <span class=\"op\">{</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb8-3\"><a href=\"#cb8-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    printf<span class=\"op\">(</span><span class=\"st\">&quot;you must connect to wifi</span><span class=\"sc\">\\n</span><span class=\"st\">&quot;</span><span class=\"op\">);</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb8-4\"><a href=\"#cb8-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"op\">}</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb8-5\"><a href=\"#cb8-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"op\">}</span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"programando-em-python\">Programando em: Python</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Podemos utilizar verifica\u00e7\u00f5es simples para avaliar cada condi\u00e7\u00e3o\nindividualmente. Valores num\u00e9ricos diferentes de zero s\u00e3o interpretados\ncomo True, enquanto zero \u00e9 considerado False. O operador not \u00e9 utilizado\npara negar uma condi\u00e7\u00e3o</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb9\"><pre class=\"sourceCode py\"><code class=\"sourceCode python\"><span id=\"cb9-1\"><a href=\"#cb9-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"cf\">if</span> <span class=\"kw\">not</span> wifi:</span>\n<span id=\"cb9-2\"><a href=\"#cb9-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"bu\">print</span>(<span class=\"st\">&quot;you must connect to wifi&quot;</span>)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"programando-em-typescript\">Programando em: TypeScript</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>podemos utilizar verifica\u00e7\u00f5es simples para avaliar cada condi\u00e7\u00e3o\nindividualmente. Valores num\u00e9ricos diferentes de zero s\u00e3o interpretados\ncomo <code>true</code> em contextos booleanos, enquanto zero \u00e9\nconsiderado <code>false</code>. O operador <code>!</code> (exclama\u00e7\u00e3o)\ninverte o valor booleano de uma express\u00e3o.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb10\"><pre\nclass=\"sourceCode ts\"><code class=\"sourceCode typescript\"><span id=\"cb10-1\"><a href=\"#cb10-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"cf\">if</span> (<span class=\"op\">!</span>wifi) {</span>\n<span id=\"cb10-2\"><a href=\"#cb10-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"bu\">console</span><span class=\"op\">.</span><span class=\"fu\">log</span>(<span class=\"st\">&quot;you must connect to wifi&quot;</span>)<span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb10-3\"><a href=\"#cb10-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>}</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"sourceCode\" id=\"cb11\"><pre\nclass=\"sourceCode ts\"><code class=\"sourceCode typescript\"><span id=\"cb11-1\"><a href=\"#cb11-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a><span class=\"cf\">if</span> (<span class=\"op\">!</span>wifi) {</span>\n<span id=\"cb11-2\"><a href=\"#cb11-2\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>    <span class=\"fu\">write</span>(<span class=\"st\">&quot;you must connect to wifi&quot;</span>)<span class=\"op\">;</span></span>\n<span id=\"cb11-3\"><a href=\"#cb11-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\"></a>}</span></code></pre></div>\n</body>\n</html>",
